ets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同你情況差唔多9成似<br />\n其實代步用/用3幾年, 咩年份, 易唔易壞又有乜所謂, 反正你都係練車, 唔係拎去威<br />\n個流程就應該係咁既, 係網度睇岩左就搵個賣家, 約一日出黎睇車試車<br />\n如果都岩你, 又想再安心D, 就約多日朝早去上架/車房CHECK下佢, 冇問題就接住去運輸處搞過牌, 同時間上網搞第三保, 有左COVERNOTE連埋D文件出牌就搞點, 即日可以揸走<br />\n<br />\n但我最後屋企人唔鐘意二手野, 買左0首車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adb5aa80057fbf4f9f90ef2f79c86913abc3c9b","tid":25432,"uid":18416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>P牌 過25歲<br />\n想出部jizz 操車<br />\n上28睇 1萬至9萬都有<br />\n上網睇過資料 好似某一年份個波檔有問題<br />\n其實budget 2萬左右 係咪無咩可能買到？<br />\n買二手車流程又係點？無朋友/相熟車房應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2萬左右jizz 係咪預3萬整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同你情況差唔多9成似<br />\n其實代步用/用3幾年, 咩年份, 易唔易壞又有乜所謂, 反正你都係練車, 唔係拎去威<br />\n個流程就應該係咁既, 係網度睇岩左就搵個賣家, 約一日出黎睇車試車<br />\n如果都岩你, 又想再安心D, 就約多日朝早去上架/車房CHECK下佢, 冇問題就接住去運輸處搞過牌, 同時間上網搞第三保, 有左COVERNOTE連埋D文件出牌就搞點, 即日可以揸走<br />\n<br />\n但我最後屋企人唔鐘意二手野, 買左0首車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks bro"},{"pid":"9aba0fd545cb43a11b54da2ca3333f5bf8085b61","tid":25432,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:48:26.000Z","msg":"Corolla nez121啦冇野整 加上jazz冇尾反而操壞手勢"},{"pid":"f3a92cb8e457304fa10be9231d5ee163cbeb7d0b","tid":25432,"uid":43899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"如果齋假日車 泊公屋停車場 一個月大約預要玩幾錢？"},{"pid":"2646c761277154d09255a81303ff58d3037aa2c8","tid":25432,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:21:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果齋假日車 泊公屋停車場 一個月大約預要玩幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你停車場平貴 再加埋油錢 一個月出幾多次車"},{"pid":"2165ed6b05f4fa41cac51eae30ed935122c261bf","tid":25432,"uid":6732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果齋假日車 泊公屋停車場 一個月大約預要玩幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你用幾多缸油啦 正常打爆一缸500蚊左右<br />\n當你用兩缸 1000蚊<br />\n公屋停車場都要睇你邊區㗎喎<br />\n當你1800蚊？<br />\n揸車出街泊車又一筆 當500蚊<br />\n<br />\n牌費 燕梳 1500cc 計 都座住6000<br />\n計埋啲日常保養 <br />\n我諗你預4000蚊到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae42426c85957da554c99cfdbb52e39ea1388657","tid":25432,"uid":43899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果齋假日車 泊公屋停車場 一個月大約預要玩幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你停車場平貴 再加埋油錢 一個月出幾多次車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係假日先出車 加埋其他雜費呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e8c67cfbf65a8228e401c944d65ab88cc5cee1","tid":25432,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>P牌 過25歲<br />\n想出部jizz 操車<br />\n上28睇 1萬至9萬都有<br />\n上網睇過資料 好似某一年份個波檔有問題<br />\n其實budget 2萬左右 係咪無咩可能買到？<br />\n買二手車流程又係點？無朋友/相熟車房應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2萬左右jizz 係咪預3萬整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry 打錯 jazz</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打少陣J 啦"},{"pid":"d5da4d8d5c470671746f87022b5a4bba89c7892d","tid":25432,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=qBthqP3FTW7irafgb228CHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=07d29590\" target=\"_blank\">http://on.cc</a>東網專訊】沙田吐露港公路發生三車串燒兩傷意外。一輛私家車，晚上近7時沿吐露港公路往九龍方向駛至科學園附近，司機因應交通情況減速停下，豈料，尾隨黃色本田Jazz收掣不及，撞向私家車尾。兩車司機準備落車理論之際，另一輛客貨車馳至，「嘭」一聲，猛力撼向Jazz，導致該車半截車身縮起，繼而衝前再一次撞及前面私家車。 <br />\n<br />\nJazz上姓李(25歲)男司機與同齡姓劉女乘客，背及腰部痛楚，同被困車內，其他司機見狀報警。消防員到場將兩名傷者救出送院，其餘兩名俱姓陳(34及54歲)男司機無恙，警方封鎖現場調查。意外引致現場交通非常擠塞，直至肇事車輛移走後，交通始恢復正常。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/081639_61be32bd9c2c969b5a546d535dd97d8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F081639_61be32bd9c2c969b5a546d535dd97d8c.jpg&h=b03b0a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Q4eEh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Q4eEh.jpg&h=ee45e969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161127/mobile/bkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161127%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001.html&d=qBthqP3FTW7irafgb228CHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a45fa65e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161127/mobile/bkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n不如一人夾幾蚊俾車主去買返個車尾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBetween架車應該仲行到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9fa69977b1ff7086cbc63fec9c7231b73fae3f7f","tid":25432,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=qBthqP3FTW7irafgb228CHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=07d29590\" target=\"_blank\">http://on.cc</a>東網專訊】沙田吐露港公路發生三車串燒兩傷意外。一輛私家車，晚上近7時沿吐露港公路往九龍方向駛至科學園附近，司機因應交通情況減速停下，豈料，尾隨黃色本田Jazz收掣不及，撞向私家車尾。兩車司機準備落車理論之際，另一輛客貨車馳至，「嘭」一聲，猛力撼向Jazz，導致該車半截車身縮起，繼而衝前再一次撞及前面私家車。 <br />\n<br />\nJazz上姓李(25歲)男司機與同齡姓劉女乘客，背及腰部痛楚，同被困車內，其他司機見狀報警。消防員到場將兩名傷者救出送院，其餘兩名俱姓陳(34及54歲)男司機無恙，警方封鎖現場調查。意外引致現場交通非常擠塞，直至肇事車輛移走後，交通始恢復正常。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/081639_61be32bd9c2c969b5a546d535dd97d8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F081639_61be32bd9c2c969b5a546d535dd97d8c.jpg&h=b03b0a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Q4eEh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Q4eEh.jpg&h=ee45e969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161127/mobile/bkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161127%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001.html&d=qBthqP3FTW7irafgb228CHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a45fa65e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161127/mobile/bkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n不如一人夾幾蚊俾車主去買返個車尾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBetween架車應該仲行到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n直版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d0104a918d6ee6dd8a11e3ab4f3d427a75e62e","tid":25432,"uid":57591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:39:35.000Z","msg":"今日先賣左部jazz俾人 P牌用黎操左兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e935d1982cda6c123a326160b3fe36eed5e0ce75","tid":25432,"uid":18416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日先賣左部jazz俾人 P牌用黎操左兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo