faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5e5dd2cbd5a83743769b31b7d5828eab6dbc09","tid":25432,"uid":56021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問，二手車有冇話買二零零幾年之後比較好？同埋行得多過十萬公里係咪比較差？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實無話嘅 係好睇上手保養成點<br />\n保養得好嘅話 9x年啲車頭都可以好精神<br />\n相反保養得唔好 1x年都可以整撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448c9c9adc01fec27fbbcaeb0bd84217ecbb926e","tid":25432,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同問，二手車有冇話買二零零幾年之後比較好？同埋行得多過十萬公里係咪比較差？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實無話嘅 係好睇上手保養成點<br />\n保養得好嘅話 9x年啲車頭都可以好精神<br />\n相反保養得唔好 1x年都可以整撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks巴打，我自己就想買二手7人，主要第一年撞下都唔心痛，我上網睇車行會唔會宰得好勁？<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下我自己21，未甩p，保險個d有冇話邊間比較好，麻煩晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9802487d811cd0eb677505c9bd2dd064c718f8e","tid":25432,"uid":56021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同問，二手車有冇話買二零零幾年之後比較好？同埋行得多過十萬公里係咪比較差？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實無話嘅 係好睇上手保養成點<br />\n保養得好嘅話 9x年啲車頭都可以好精神<br />\n相反保養得唔好 1x年都可以整撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks巴打，我自己就想買二手7人，主要第一年撞下都唔心痛，我上網睇車行會唔會宰得好勁？<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下我自己21，未甩p，保險個d有冇話邊間比較好，麻煩晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為車行唔好搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既然車行賣得比你嘅車價賺到錢嘅<br />\n咁你係私人買賣一定可以買到呢個價錢甚至更平<br />\n<br />\n未甩p未夠歲我一定唔會諗自己出保險<br />\n除非你好有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}